@startuml BE4_CreateAccount_StateChart
hide empty description

[*] --> displayCreateAccountPage
displayCreateAccountPage : display relevant account creation page

displayCreateAccountPage --> validateInputs : required information entered
validateInputs : validate account information

validateInputs --> accountError : information is missing or invalid
accountError : display error message
accountError --> displayCreateAccountPage : retry

validateInputs --> checkRoleRequirements : inputs valid
checkRoleRequirements : determine requested role requirements

checkRoleRequirements --> requestVerification : role requires verification
requestVerification : send request for verification

requestVerification --> recordFailureEvent : verification fails
recordFailureEvent : record failure in audit logs
recordFailureEvent --> accountError : notify user

requestVerification --> createAccount : verification succeeds
checkRoleRequirements --> createAccount : no verification required

createAccount : create account with role and RBAC permissions
createAccount --> recordFailureEvent : account creation fails
createAccount --> confirmAccountCreation : account created

confirmAccountCreation : confirm account creation and prompt Log In
confirmAccountCreation --> recordAccountCreationEvent

recordAccountCreationEvent : record account creation event in audit logs
recordAccountCreationEvent --> [*]

@enduml